Project Description 
Title: Bob the encounter builder
Description: met Bob de encounter builder willen we er voor zorgen dat gamemasters makkelijk zelf custom monsters kunnen maken en deze delen met hun peers.
Ook willen we er voor zorgen dat de game masters makkelijk een random encountertable kunnen maken met hun homebrew monsters

As a gamemaster
I'm able to create homebrew monsters
So that I can see the monsters I created

Acceptance criteria:
a monster should be saved in the database and be displayed in the monster list

As a user
I'm able to see all monsters
So that I can get inspiration form other people's monsters

Acceptance criteria:
as a logged in user of the page i am able to see the monster list page and search for monsters

As a gamemaster 
I'm able to update an encountertable
So that I can see what the random encounter is that i rolled

Acceptance criteria: as a gamemaster when i create the encountertable i should see it

As a gamemaster 
I'm able to delete an action to monster
So that I can see them in the monster descreption

Acceptance criteria: when a gamemaster creates an action to the monster it should be displayed in the monster description

